All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler, DeclHandler, EntityResolver2, LexicalHandler
public class SaxParserDeclHandler
extends DefaultHandler2
implements DeclHandler

An instance of this class is registered with the SAX parser to handle events related to the XML document's DTD declarations. In this application, the information about parsed internal and external entity declarations is captured
